        <tr><td>9–12</td><td>Structured programme — see below</td><td>45–60 min</td><td>4–5</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p>This progression may feel too easy at first. That's intentional — building the habit of showing up consistently is the goal of weeks 1–4, not fitness improvement.</p>
